{"tid":823942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹過後】林鄭昨晚FB：舒一口氣　政府今早提醒市民「預留足夠時間出行」","createTime":"2018-09-17T02:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T02:41:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bc15ad17aba11035f7677dfe67fab2ddb44bdcc4","tid":823942,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180917/s00001/f09b0942938bc42b201e37b569fee77c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2Ff09b0942938bc42b201e37b569fee77c.jpg&h=c4f1b989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「山竹」威力強勁，天文台昨日發出去年8月以來首個10號風球，歷時10小時，各部門嚴陣以待。至昨晚7時40分改發8號風球，特首林鄭月娥亦在facebook發帖指「大家都舒一口氣」，惟提醒仍須保持警覺，「唔好咁快鬆懈」。<br />\n<br />\n颱風「山竹」過後，本港滿目瘡痍。塌樹堵塞道路等問題嚴重，加上交通網絡及設施受到不少破壞，今早大部分巴士路線、站分鐵路及橫水渡等仍然停駛，政府今早透過新聞處發稿，提醒市民要留意道路情況及公共運輸服務最新安排，並「預留足夠時間出行」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180917/s00001/1537142429900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F1537142429900&d=KPPkmUstXgKNlaWvbQeyJo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f39a1ffc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F1537142429900&h=eb5dc814\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180917/s00001/1537142429900</a>"},{"pid":"2734827d35bbda196de9a80f0e8ae3e24d289d36","tid":823942,"uid":3873,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/101052_e151c9ed38d191e5f0c8604663c7e25a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F101052_e151c9ed38d191e5f0c8604663c7e25a.jpg&h=e6dbff75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af5cee4efb01a92fc3b0cf7b